author: By SAM McNEIL Associated Press
title: VIRUS DIARY: In Beijing, finally, a tentative spring blooms
description: BEIJING (AP) — The coronavirus came first in the depths of winter. As with so many places afterward, the change seeped in gradually.
content:
BEIJING (AP) The coronavirus came first in the depths of winter. As with so many places afterward, the change seeped in gradually.
